<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Game Plan - Your Ultimate Sports Management Platform</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-dark: #0B2447;
            --primary-medium: #19376D;
            --primary-light: #576CBC;
            --accent-light: #A5D7E8;
            --text-light: #E6F4F1;
            --spacing-xs: 0.5rem;
            --spacing-sm: 1rem;
            --spacing-md: 1.5rem;
            --spacing-lg: 2rem;
            --spacing-xl: 3rem;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary-medium), var(--primary-light));
            color: var(--text-light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background: rgba(11, 36, 71, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: var(--spacing-md) 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0px;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-light);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(165, 215, 232, 0.5);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-left: 0px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            padding-left: 15px;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .nav-btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-light), var(--primary-medium));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-medium), var(--primary-light));
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        main {
            margin-top: 100px;
            flex: 1;
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .hero {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: var(--spacing-xl);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-light);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: var(--spacing-lg);
            padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--accent-light);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Footer Styles */
        footer {
            background: rgba(11, 36, 71, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: var(--spacing-md) 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: var(--spacing-md);
            }

            nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 100%;
            }

            .nav-btn {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .logo h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .tagline {
                margin-left: 20px;
                padding-left: 10px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: var(--spacing-lg);
            }

            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container header-content">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>Game Plan</h1>
                <div class="tagline">Where Sports Meets Strategy</div>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <a href="/login" class="nav-btn">Login</a>
                <a href="/signup" class="nav-btn">Sign Up</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <section class="hero">
                <h2>Welcome to Game Plan</h2>
                <p>Experience seamless sports session management with our innovative platform. Create, join, and
                    organize sports activities with ease.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>For Organizers</h3>
                    <p>Powerful tools to manage sports sessions, track activities, and generate comprehensive reports
                        with ease.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>For Players</h3>
                    <p>Join sessions, manage your schedule, and connect with other players in your community
                        effortlessly.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Game Plan. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>